    <item>
      <title>菲律宾因六月海上冲突向中国索赔 100 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/philippines-demanding-1-million-from-china-over-june-sea-clash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方负责人罗密欧·布劳纳周四表示，菲律宾要求中国赔偿上个月在南海发生的冲突造成的 6000 万比索（100 万美元）的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/philippines-demanding-1-million-from-china-over-june-sea-clash</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 03:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾老龄化加剧 进一步放宽外籍看护限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/faster-aging-taiwan-further-eases-curbs-on-foreign-caregivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于历史性的低出生率导致老年人难以找到长期支持，台湾将放宽雇用外籍住家保姆的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/faster-aging-taiwan-further-eases-curbs-on-foreign-caregivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大不顾美国报复威胁实施数字服务税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国警告称将采取贸易报复措施，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府仍批准对大型外国科技公司征收数字服务税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾情报局长称中国扣押船只可能是出于政治原因</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/taiwan-spy-chief-says-politics-may-be-reason-china-seized-boat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾情报部门负责人称，中国本周扣押一艘台湾渔船可能出于政治动机，并称此举可能是对民主台湾施压的一种方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/taiwan-spy-chief-says-politics-may-be-reason-china-seized-boat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一些参议院民主党人对拜登的政治前途表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/senate-democrat-breaks-ranks-airs-concerns-about-biden-s-odds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位民主党参议员表示，几位参议院民主党人私下表示，在上周灾难性的辩论之后，他们认为拜登总统在政治上没有生存的余地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/senate-democrat-breaks-ranks-airs-concerns-about-biden-s-odds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在危机会议后赢得民主党州长的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-wins-democratic-governors-backing-after-crisis-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在白宫举行的危机会议后，主要民主党州长对总统乔·拜登及其竞选连任表示了迄今为止最强烈​​的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/biden-wins-democratic-governors-backing-after-crisis-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 00:20:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登难以抑制退出竞选的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，《纽约时报》报道称，乔·拜登已将退出美国总统竞选的可能性拱手让给了一位关键盟友，而民主党内部也出现了要求他退出的运动，这进一步加剧了要求拜登退出美国总统竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平支持普京，北京面临结束乌克兰战争的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管西方国家政府对于中国支持莫斯科的战争努力日益感到不满，但国家主席习近平仍坚持中俄关系，并重申了北京在乌克兰问题上的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/putin-meets-xi-for-second-time-since-may-as-leaders-hail-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:42:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
